{"id": 2894, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都有哪些“结果强迫症”？", "description": "哪些时候，你会对一件事的“结果”特别在意？（题图来自：iStock ©️ FoxysGraphic）", "record_count": 8459, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190415160808vgYGOzpkXePRNqlQ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5684, "title": "你都有哪些“结果强迫症”？", "content": "你都有哪些“结果强迫症”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 339307, "content": "读文章一定要总结要点，否则会忘记刚才看了啥", "image": "img/option/option/20190415192448X5ID0cqZoyM9LEYe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339308, "content": "看到某个新闻，一定要（结合多方意见）归纳出结论", "image": "img/option/option/20190415195412Mt46hGQ0zFoT5KEA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339309, "content": "追的剧就算烂尾，还是会习惯性用两倍速刷完", "image": "img/option/option/20190415192813QZs5f7CKD4Ru0zbk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339312, "content": "系列电影的前几部不看没关系，但大结局一定要看", "image": "img/option/option/201904151932270Ndg152QaBbXGpmc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339315, "content": "看剧时出现新角色，总想尽快确定“这是好人还是坏人”", "image": "img/option/option/20190415193409JNrMinZScDYuQybe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339323, "content": "线上聊天，不说再见/晚安就会觉得“这嗑还没唠完”", "image": "img/option/option/201904151935056lV1c3R95TSudh08.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339330, "content": "宁可花时间做点无谓的事，也绝不能让自己“闲着”", "image": "img/option/option/20190415193553zlA47w1G5iEmpaO3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 339336, "content": "工作一天没啥成果，就会觉得“我是不是在瞎忙”", "image": "img/option/option/20190415193809wSPjd6LvZK49ITNh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}